    "client_msg_id": "70544F9B-3800-4B55-9836-706088B49409",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Yesterday, I finished reading <@UEH6T3RJB>’s paper _An Anatomy of Interaction: Co-occurrences and Entanglements_ <https://www.shift-society.org/salon/papers/2018/revised/anatomy-of-interaction-authorversion.pdf>.\n\nToday, I just read ribbonfarm’s blog post _Worlding Raga: 5 — World How?_ <https://www.ribbonfarm.com/2019/04/25/worlding-raga-5-world-how/>.\n\nIn a strange way for me these two resonate with overlapping frequencies creating beautiful harmony, although I can’t quite put my finger on what exactly makes me think that.",
